c host the VM is running on","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"message"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"string","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Human-readable status message","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lastTransitionTime"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"string","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"ISO 8601 timestamp","type":"text"}]}]]]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Printer-Columns","text":"Printer Columns"},{"code":["kubectl get mvm","# NAME        PHASE     IP              NODE     AGE","# runner-01   Running   192.168.64.3    mac-01   5m","# runner-02   Running   192.168.64.4    mac-01   3m"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Examples","text":"Examples"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"GitHub-Actions-Runner","text":"GitHub Actions Runner"},{"code":["apiVersion: spooktacular.app\/v1alpha1","kind: MacOSVM","metadata:","  name: gha-runner-01","spec:","  sourceVM: base","  cpu: 4","  memoryInGigabytes: 8","  ephemeral: true","  template: github-runner","  provisioning:","    mode: ssh","    script: |","      #!\/bin\/bash","      cd \/Users\/admin","      curl -o actions-runner.tar.gz -L \\","        https:\/\/github.com\/actions\/runner\/releases\/latest\/download\/actions-runner-osx-arm64-2.x.x.tar.gz","      tar xzf actions-runner.tar.gz","      .\/config.sh --url https:\/\/github.com\/your-org\/repo \\","        --token YOUR_TOKEN --ephemeral","      .\/run.sh"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"yaml"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"See ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"deploy\/kubernetes\/examples\/github-runner.yaml"},{"text":" for the full example.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Remote-Desktop","text":"Remote Desktop"},{"code":["apiVersion: spooktacular.app\/v1alpha1","kind: MacOSVM","metadata:","  name: desktop-01","spec:","  sourceVM: base","  cpu: 8","  memoryInGigabytes: 16","  template: remote-desktop","  network: \"bridged:en0\""],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"yaml"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"See ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"deploy\/kubernetes\/examples\/remote-desktop.yaml"},{"text":" for the full example.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Ephemeral-Runner-Pool","text":"Ephemeral Runner Pool"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Create multiple ephemeral runners using a multi-document YAML:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["kubectl apply -f deploy\/kubernetes\/examples\/ephemeral-pool.yaml"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This creates 3 runners that auto-destroy after each job completes.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Controller-Details","text":"Controller Details"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Swift controller (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sources\/spook-controller\/"},{"text":") consists of:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KubernetesClient"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — Reads service account credentials,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"makes authenticated requests to the K8s API"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Reconciler"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — List+watch pattern with auto-reconnection."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Handles ADDED (clone+start), MODIFIED (retry\/resolve IP),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and DELETED (stop+delete) events"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"NodeManager"}]},{"type":"text","t